Commentary Text: Moeen Ali to J Richardson, out Bowled!! How has he missed this? Probably a little eager to put the half-tracker away? Was it a half-tracker at all? It's short for sure, but maybe not as much as Richardson thinks as he rocks back to pull. He's gone through the shot a little early and the ball sneaks through to crash into the stumps. Just when a partnership was building, Richardson has thrown it away. J Richardson b Moeen Ali 15(22) [4s-2]
